Lisa and James Tuttle and her family moved to Geldeston in Norfolk in 2005 with their five children . 
  Their dogs Marley and Lily were shot dead by the farmer next door in 2014 . 
  They were accused of slaughtering his birds after escaping onto his land . 
  The Tuttle family had a long-running dispute with John Cook . 
  Their first dog Ruby had to be re-homed because she kept escaping from their garden . 
  Mr Cook shot the dogs after accusing them of killing his birds . 
 